---
import BaseHead from '../../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';
import Header from '../../components/Header.astro';
import { SITE_DESCRIPTION } from '../../consts';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<BaseHead title='Minah Tak' description={SITE_DESCRIPTION} />
		<style>
			@import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:wght@400;600&family=Inter:wght@300;400;500&display=swap');
			
			* {
				margin: 0;
				padding: 0;
				box-sizing: border-box;
			}

			body {
				background-color: #ffffff;
				color: #000000;
				font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, sans-serif;
				line-height: 1.6;
			}

			main {
				width: 100%;
				max-width: 900px;
				margin: 0 auto;
				padding: 8rem 2rem 4rem;
				min-height: 80vh;
			}

			/* Hero Section */
			.hero {
				margin-bottom: 8rem;
				display: grid;
				grid-template-columns: 1fr 200px;
				gap: 4rem;
				align-items: start;
			}

			.hero-content {
				padding-top: 1rem;
			}

			.hero-image-container {
				position: relative;
			}

			.hero-image {
				width: 200px;
				height: 200px;
				border-radius: 50%;
				object-fit: cover;
				border: 3px solid #000000;
				box-shadow: 12px 12px 0 rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
			}

			.hero-image-decoration {
				position: absolute;
				width: 100%;
				height: 100%;
				border: 2px solid #000000;
				border-radius: 50%;
				top: -15px;
				left: -15px;
				z-index: -1;
			}

			.hero-title {
				font-family: 'Playfair Display', Georgia, serif;
				font-size: clamp(3.5rem, 10vw, 7rem);
				font-weight: 400;
				letter-spacing: -0.02em;
				line-height: 1.1;
				margin-bottom: 3rem;
				color: #000000;
			}

			.hero-description {
				font-size: 1.125rem;
				font-weight: 300;
				line-height: 1.8;
				max-width: 600px;
				color: #333333;
				margin-bottom: 2rem;
			}

			.hero-cta {
				display: inline-block;
				padding: 0.875rem 2rem;
				background-color: #000000;
				color: #ffffff;
				text-decoration: none;
				font-size: 0.9rem;
				font-weight: 400;
				letter-spacing: 0.05em;
				text-transform: uppercase;
				transition: all 0.3s ease;
				border: 2px solid #000000;
				position: relative;
				overflow: hidden;
			}

			.hero-cta::before {
				content: '';
				position: absolute;
				top: 0;
				left: -100%;
				width: 100%;
				height: 100%;
				background-color: #ffffff;
				transition: left 0.3s ease;
				z-index: 0;
			}

			.hero-cta:hover::before {
				left: 0;
			}

			.hero-cta:hover {
				color: #000000;
			}

			.hero-cta span {
				position: relative;
				z-index: 1;
			}

			.hero-stats {
				display: flex;
				gap: 3rem;
				margin-top: 3rem;
				padding-top: 2rem;
				border-top: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
			}

			.stat-item {
				display: flex;
				flex-direction: column;
				gap: 0.25rem;
			}

			.stat-number {
				font-family: 'Playfair Display', Georgia, serif;
				font-size: 2rem;
				font-weight: 600;
				color: #000000;
			}

			.stat-label {
				text-transform: uppercase;
				letter-spacing: 0.1em;
				font-size: 0.75rem;
				color: #999999;
			}

			/* Navigation Grid */
			.nav-grid {
				display: grid;
				grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
				gap: 1px;
				background-color: #e0e0e0;
				border: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
				margin-bottom: 6rem;
			}

			.nav-card {
				background: #ffffff;
				padding: 3rem 2rem;
				text-decoration: none;
				color: inherit;
				transition: all 0.3s ease;
				position: relative;
				overflow: hidden;
			}

			.nav-card::before {
				content: '';
				position: absolute;
				top: 0;
				left: 0;
				width: 0;
				height: 2px;
				background: #000000;
				transition: width 0.3s ease;
			}

			.nav-card:hover::before {
				width: 100%;
			}

			.nav-card:hover {
				background: #fafafa;
			}

			.nav-card h3 {
				font-family: 'Playfair Display', Georgia, serif;
				font-size: 1.75rem;
				font-weight: 400;
				margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
				color: #000000;
			}

			.nav-card p {
				font-size: 0.9rem;
				font-weight: 300;
				color: #666666;
				line-height: 1.6;
			}

			/* Footer note */
			.footer-note {
				text-align: center;
				font-size: 0.875rem;
				color: #999999;
				font-weight: 300;
				padding: 4rem 0;
				border-top: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
			}

			@media (max-width: 768px) {
				main {
					padding: 4rem 1.5rem 3rem;
				}

				.hero {
					grid-template-columns: 1fr;
					gap: 3rem;
				}

				.hero-image-container {
					order: -1;
					margin: 0 auto;
				}

				.hero-image {
					width: 150px;
					height: 150px;
				}

				.hero-title {
					margin-bottom: 2rem;
				}

				.hero-stats {
					flex-wrap: wrap;
					gap: 2rem;
				}

				.nav-grid {
					grid-template-columns: 1fr;
				}

				.nav-card {
					padding: 2.5rem 1.5rem;
				}
			}
		</style>
	</head>
	<body>
		<Header />
		<main>
			<section class="hero">
				<div class="hero-content">
					<h1 class="hero-title">Minah Tak</h1>
					
					<p class="hero-description">
						공부하면서 이것저것 만드는 학생입니다.
						아이디어만 잔뜩 있고 실력은 키우는 중이에요.
						코드도 굽고(?) 쿠키도 굽고,
						망해본 경험도 차곡차곡 기록합니다.
					</p>

					<a href="/me" class="hero-cta">
						<span>The Full Story →</span>
					</a>

					<div class="hero-stats">
						<div class="stat-item">
							<div class="stat-number">∞</div>
							<div class="stat-label">Questions</div>
						</div>
						<div class="stat-item">
							<div class="stat-number">v1.0</div>
							<div class="stat-label">Always</div>
						</div>
						<div class="stat-item">
							<div class="stat-number">0→1</div>
							<div class="stat-label">Mindset</div>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>

				<div class="hero-image-container">
					<div class="hero-image-decoration"></div>
					<img 
						src="../../src/assets/MinahTak_Profile.jpg" 
						alt="Minah Tak" 
						class="hero-image"
					/>
				</div>
			</section>

			<nav class="nav-grid">
				<a href="/explore" class="nav-card">
					<h3>Explore</h3>
					<p>새벽 탐험, 샤워 중 번뜩인 생각들, 잠 못 이루게 만드는 질문들</p>
				</a>

				<a href="/builds" class="nav-card">
					<h3>Builds</h3>
					<p>반쯤 구운 아이디어를 현실로. 어떤 건 되고, 어떤 건 안 되고. 그래도 배워가는 중!</p>
				</a>

				<a href="/ko/blog" class="nav-card">
					<h3>Logs</h3>
					<p>일상 기록 : 타버린 식빵, 버그투성이 코드, 그 사이 모든 순간</p>
				</a>

				<a href="/me" class="nav-card">
					<h3>About me</h3>
					<p>코딩 안 할 때의 모습. (아마 여전히 디버깅 중일 확률 99%)</p>
				</a>
			</nav>

		</main>
		<Footer />
	</body>
</html>